<i>adverb</i>: 중히 [중ː히], 귀히 [귀ː히], 귀중히 [귀ː중히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>중히 [중ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. preciously</dd><br>
<dd>매우 중요하고 소중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With respect and care.</dd><br>
<dd>2. severely</dd><br>
<dd>대단하거나 크게. 또는 무겁게.</dd><br>
<dd>Greatly, seriously or gravely.</dd><br>
<dt>귀히 [귀ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. nobly</dd><br>
<dd>신분이나 지위 등이 높게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being in a high position, status, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. valuably; preciously</dd><br>
<dd>아주 가치가 있고 소중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner which conveys that something is precious and valuable.</dd><br>
<dt>귀중히 [귀ː중히]</dt><br>
<dd>valuably; preciously</dd><br>
<dd>귀하고 중요하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With care and love.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>